  "detailed_description": "<i>A fascinating clicker about a journalist's journey through the homes of the most popular people around the world. In this game you will visit different countries and cities, visiting celebrities. Accumulate gold to buy the necessary resources, collect foreign passports to travel from one country to another. <br><br><i>Imagine yourself as a journalist traveling the homes of the world's most popular people.  Get passports to fly from country to country.  Earn gold to buy everything you need.</i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>In this game you will find:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><u>Unique </u>activities, including:</li></ul><i>- Defense of the White House <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1517230/extras/8d3cd64c7cf4940487034573c325baff.webp?t=1614450735\" width=40 height=40 /></span><br>- Coin Catcher <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1517230/extras/252d65dfc893aa12aef336fe9e634824.webp?t=1614450735\" width=40 height=40 /></span><br>- Battle of the views <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1517230/extras/fa341001fa24aa3e141aa17b09a755b1.webp?t=1614450735\" width=40 height=40 /></span><br><br>- And much more</i><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><u>A well-designed </u>economic system  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1517230/extras/2f0de5d1fdaa8e5c39fbf7ef43647621.webp?t=1614450735\" width=40 height=40 /></span><br></li><li>The main currency is \"<u>Gold</u>\"  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1517230/extras/b3ae441b67ccc4fc35eed4cb29abbd78.webp?t=1614450735\" width=40 height=40 /></span><br></li><li><u>Large </u>selection of music  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1517230/extras/c757e7dd1e6ea3919b111cbaed70e59f.webp?t=1614450735\" width=40 height=40 /></span><br><br></li><li>Some of the most <u>popular </u>people in the world<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1517230/extras/955bc601003f9489739bd2e8f7d5ba0e.webp?t=1614450735\" width=40 height=40 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1517230/extras/3148874df82caebe9004b5031544adac.webp?t=1614450735\" width=40 height=40 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1517230/extras/3e4f8bac30d0b84964bd9af7341a57a7.webp?t=1614450735\" width=40 height=40 /></span></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Gameplay Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A diverse selection of vehicles  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1517230/extras/abe929ba5a84bfb338f1329c59152af0.webp?t=1614450735\" width=40 height=40 /></span><br></li><li>Bonus system for in-game currency  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1517230/extras/0ae6b2e41b2878330bf022e100a3275d.webp?t=1614450735\" width=40 height=40 /></span><br></li><li>A soundtrack that emphasizes the style of the game  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1517230/extras/c757e7dd1e6ea3919b111cbaed70e59f.webp?t=1614450735\" width=40 height=40 /></span></li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=